# ToolDash Website

This repository hosts the source for **ToolDash**, an on‑demand tool rental and job‑site delivery platform.

## 🌐 Live Site
Once GitHub Pages is enabled, your site will be here:
```
https://braxtonjterrebonne.github.io/tooldashwebsite/
```

## 📂 Repo Structure
- `index.html` — main landing page (built with Tailwind via CDN, mobile‑friendly)
- `404.html` — not found page for GitHub Pages
- `README.md` — project documentation

## 🚀 Deployment
1. Commit changes to `main` branch.
2. In GitHub: **Settings → Pages → Branch: main → / (root)**.
3. Wait 1–2 minutes for GitHub Pages to publish.

## ✨ Features
- Responsive landing page with Hero, About, Services, Contact sections
- Sticky header + mobile navigation
- Formspree integration (replace placeholder endpoint)
- SEO/OG tags and social preview image support
- Custom 404 page
- Favicon and social preview image template

## 🔧 Setup Notes
- Replace `/favicon.ico` in the repo root with your actual favicon.
- Swap in your real Formspree form ID or backend endpoint for contact form.
- Update brand colors in the Tailwind config (top of `index.html`) as needed.
- Replace `social-card.png` with a branded preview image and update `og:image` in `index.html`.

